  "content": {
    "en": "<p data-start=\"117\" data-end=\"200\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><strong data-start=\"117\" data-end=\"200\">Modern food delivery website with an admin panel and automated order management</strong></p><hr data-start=\"202\" data-end=\"205\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1ppn3ms\" data-start=\"207\" data-end=\"227\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><span data-cms-image=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okcompany/web-studio/main/apps/web/public/uploads/img_1777642385302_6795.png\" data-cms-filename=\"222.png\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"cms-image-token\">[222.png]</span>About the Project</h2><p data-start=\"229\" data-end=\"494\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\">A full-featured web solution for an Italian delivery restaurant in Siegen, Germany.<br data-start=\"312\" data-end=\"315\">The system allows customers to browse the menu, build a cart, and place orders, while the administrator can manage content, receive notifications, and process orders in real time.</p><p data-start=\"496\" data-end=\"556\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><span data-cms-image=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okcompany/web-studio/main/apps/web/public/uploads/img_1777642397240_8456.png\" data-cms-filename=\"333.png\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"cms-image-token\">[333.png]</span>🔗 <strong data-start=\"499\" data-end=\"516\">Live website:</strong> <a data-start=\"517\" data-end=\"556\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_new\" class=\"decorated-link\" href=\"https://pizza-roma-siegen-v2.vercel.app\">https://pizza-roma-siegen-v2.vercel.app<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-rtl-flip=\"\" class=\"block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]\"><use href=\"/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#304883\" fill=\"currentColor\"></use></svg></span></a></p><hr data-start=\"558\" data-end=\"561\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1fhtv5l\" data-start=\"563\" data-end=\"582\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\">Website Features</h2><h3 data-section-id=\"151hcol\" data-start=\"584\" data-end=\"605\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\">🛍️ For Customers</h3><ul data-start=\"606\" data-end=\"862\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><li data-section-id=\"1fazz6b\" data-start=\"606\" data-end=\"661\">User-friendly cart with toppings and size selection</li><li data-section-id=\"oqjehm\" data-start=\"662\" data-end=\"711\">Language switching between German and Russian</li><li data-section-id=\"tnymc3\" data-start=\"712\" data-end=\"764\"><span data-cms-image=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okcompany/web-studio/main/apps/web/public/uploads/img_1777642411538_6777.png\" data-cms-filename=\"444.png\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"cms-image-token\">[444.png]</span>Display of current promotions and special offers</li><li data-section-id=\"nvatvv\" data-start=\"765\" data-end=\"811\">Information about delivery zones and costs</li><li data-section-id=\"1r2myuk\" data-start=\"812\" data-end=\"862\">Order checkout with bot protection (reCAPTCHA)</li></ul><hr data-start=\"864\" data-end=\"867\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><h3 data-section-id=\"1fbxihv\" data-start=\"869\" data-end=\"894\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><span data-cms-image=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okcompany/web-studio/main/apps/web/public/uploads/img_1777642421294_4835.png\" data-cms-filename=\"555.png\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"cms-image-token\">[555.png]</span>⚙️ For Administrators</h3><ul data-start=\"895\" data-end=\"1128\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><li data-section-id=\"1whgu10\" data-start=\"895\" data-end=\"937\">Secure admin panel with authentication</li><li data-section-id=\"53dmz8\" data-start=\"938\" data-end=\"1001\">Real-time editing of menu, prices, descriptions, and images</li><li data-section-id=\"12rze69\" data-start=\"1002\" data-end=\"1042\">Order management with status updates</li><li data-section-id=\"tsejfa\" data-start=\"1043\" data-end=\"1092\">Instant Telegram notifications for new orders</li><li data-section-id=\"aogp1o\" data-start=\"1093\" data-end=\"1128\">Automatic saving of all changes</li></ul><hr data-start=\"1130\" data-end=\"1133\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1tfww4l\" data-start=\"1135\" data-end=\"1150\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><span data-cms-image=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okcompany/web-studio/main/apps/web/public/uploads/img_1777642434410_7243.png\" data-cms-filename=\"666.png\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"cms-image-token\">[666.png]</span>Technologies</h2><p data-start=\"1152\" data-end=\"1284\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><strong data-start=\"1152\" data-end=\"1187\">Next.js 14 + React + TypeScript</strong><br data-start=\"1187\" data-end=\"1190\">A modern tech stack with server-side rendering for fast loading and excellent SEO performance.</p><p data-start=\"1286\" data-end=\"1360\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><strong data-start=\"1286\" data-end=\"1307\">Responsive Design</strong><br data-start=\"1307\" data-end=\"1310\">Optimized for mobile, tablet, and desktop devices.</p><p data-start=\"1362\" data-end=\"1452\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><strong data-start=\"1362\" data-end=\"1383\">Smooth Animations</strong><br data-start=\"1383\" data-end=\"1386\">Framer Motion provides clean transitions and interactive elements.</p><p data-start=\"1454\" data-end=\"1552\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><strong data-start=\"1454\" data-end=\"1479\">Reliable Data Storage</strong><br data-start=\"1479\" data-end=\"1482\">Menu data is stored in GitHub, ensuring it is not lost during updates.</p><hr data-start=\"1554\" data-end=\"1557\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"18bo04s\" data-start=\"1559\" data-end=\"1568\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\">Result</h2><p data-start=\"1570\" data-end=\"1764\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\">A fully operational food delivery platform with complete functionality.<br data-start=\"1641\" data-end=\"1644\">Customers can easily place orders, while the restaurant efficiently manages everything through an intuitive admin panel.</p><hr data-start=\"1766\" data-end=\"1769\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p data-start=\"1771\" data-end=\"1842\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><em data-start=\"1771\" data-end=\"1842\">The project was developed as a complete solution for a real business.</em></p>",
    "ru": "<p data-start=\"143\" data-end=\"240\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><strong data-start=\"143\" data-end=\"240\">Современный сайт доставки еды с административной панелью и автоматизацией управления заказами</strong></p><hr data-start=\"242\" data-end=\"245\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"p47tnm\" data-start=\"247\" data-end=\"259\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><span data-cms-image=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okcompany/web-studio/main/apps/web/public/uploads/img_1777642594888_4312.png\" data-cms-filename=\"222.png\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"cms-image-token\">[222.png]</span>О проекте</h2><p data-start=\"261\" data-end=\"546\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\">Полнофункциональное веб-решение для итальянского ресторана доставки в городе Зиген, Германия.<br data-start=\"354\" data-end=\"357\"><span data-cms-image=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okcompany/web-studio/main/apps/web/public/uploads/img_1777642605921_1065.png\" data-cms-filename=\"333.png\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"cms-image-token\">[333.png]</span>Система позволяет клиентам просматривать меню, формировать корзину и оформлять заказы, а администратору — управлять контентом, получать уведомления и обрабатывать заказы в реальном времени.</p><p data-start=\"548\" data-end=\"606\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><span data-cms-image=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okcompany/web-studio/main/apps/web/public/uploads/img_1777642617059_4124.png\" data-cms-filename=\"444.png\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"cms-image-token\">[444.png]</span>🔗 <strong data-start=\"551\" data-end=\"566\">Живой сайт:</strong> <a data-start=\"567\" data-end=\"606\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_new\" class=\"decorated-link\" href=\"https://pizza-roma-siegen-v2.vercel.app\">https://pizza-roma-siegen-v2.vercel.app<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-rtl-flip=\"\" class=\"block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]\"><use href=\"/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#304883\" fill=\"currentColor\"></use></svg></span></a></p><hr data-start=\"608\" data-end=\"611\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"o6t7yg\" data-start=\"613\" data-end=\"633\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\">Возможности сайта</h2><h3 data-section-id=\"ovyecm\" data-start=\"635\" data-end=\"655\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\">🛍️ Для клиентов</h3><ul data-start=\"656\" data-end=\"921\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><li data-section-id=\"1m70g12\" data-start=\"656\" data-end=\"718\">Удобная корзина с выбором размеров и добавлением топпингов</li><li data-section-id=\"18o1qyb\" data-start=\"719\" data-end=\"768\">Переключение между немецким и русским языками</li><li data-section-id=\"v8v6rr\" data-start=\"769\" data-end=\"824\">Просмотр актуальных акций и специальных предложений</li><li data-section-id=\"acc3mg\" data-start=\"825\" data-end=\"868\">Информация о зонах доставки и стоимости</li><li data-section-id=\"i10btd\" data-start=\"869\" data-end=\"921\">Оформление заказа с защитой от ботов (reCAPTCHA)</li></ul><hr data-start=\"923\" data-end=\"926\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><h3 data-section-id=\"865abu\" data-start=\"928\" data-end=\"953\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><span data-cms-image=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okcompany/web-studio/main/apps/web/public/uploads/img_1777642632578_4111.png\" data-cms-filename=\"555.png\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"cms-image-token\">[555.png]</span>⚙️ Для администратора</h3><ul data-start=\"954\" data-end=\"1231\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><li data-section-id=\"fez3if\" data-start=\"954\" data-end=\"1007\">Защищённая административная панель с авторизацией</li><li data-section-id=\"v9wlti\" data-start=\"1008\" data-end=\"1079\">Редактирование меню, цен, описаний и изображений в реальном времени</li><li data-section-id=\"l7ij24\" data-start=\"1080\" data-end=\"1128\"><span data-cms-image=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okcompany/web-studio/main/apps/web/public/uploads/img_1777642642092_4801.png\" data-cms-filename=\"666.png\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"cms-image-token\">[666.png]</span>Управление заказами и обновление их статусов</li><li data-section-id=\"32rphw\" data-start=\"1129\" data-end=\"1186\">Мгновенные уведомления о новых заказах через Telegram</li><li data-section-id=\"1sqq7cx\" data-start=\"1187\" data-end=\"1231\">Автоматическое сохранение всех изменений</li></ul><hr data-start=\"1233\" data-end=\"1236\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"jchcy\" data-start=\"1238\" data-end=\"1251\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\">Технологии</h2><p data-start=\"1253\" data-end=\"1401\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><strong data-start=\"1253\" data-end=\"1288\">Next.js 14 + React + TypeScript</strong><br data-start=\"1288\" data-end=\"1291\">Современный стек с серверным рендерингом, обеспечивающий высокую скорость загрузки и отличную SEO-оптимизацию.</p><p data-start=\"1403\" data-end=\"1490\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><strong data-start=\"1403\" data-end=\"1424\">Адаптивный дизайн</strong><br data-start=\"1424\" data-end=\"1427\">Оптимизирован для смартфонов, планшетов и настольных устройств.</p><p data-start=\"1492\" data-end=\"1581\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><strong data-start=\"1492\" data-end=\"1512\">Плавные анимации</strong><br data-start=\"1512\" data-end=\"1515\">Framer Motion обеспечивает современные переходы и интерактивность.</p><p data-start=\"1583\" data-end=\"1677\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><strong data-start=\"1583\" data-end=\"1611\">Надёжное хранение данных</strong><br data-start=\"1611\" data-end=\"1614\">Данные меню сохраняются в GitHub и не теряются при обновлениях.</p><hr data-start=\"1679\" data-end=\"1682\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1h7yher\" data-start=\"1684\" data-end=\"1696\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\">Результат</h2><p data-start=\"1698\" data-end=\"1899\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\">Полностью готовая к работе платформа доставки с полным набором функций.<br data-start=\"1769\" data-end=\"1772\">Клиенты могут быстро и удобно оформлять заказы, а ресторан эффективно управляет всеми процессами через административную панель.</p><hr data-start=\"1901\" data-end=\"1904\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p data-start=\"1906\" data-end=\"1972\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><em data-start=\"1906\" data-end=\"1972\">Проект разработан как полноценное решение для реального бизнеса.</em></p>",
    "de": "<p data-start=\"120\" data-end=\"226\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><strong data-start=\"120\" data-end=\"226\">Moderne Website für einen Lieferservice mit Administrationspanel und automatisierter Bestellabwicklung</strong></p><hr data-start=\"228\" data-end=\"231\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1m3mdmv\" data-start=\"233\" data-end=\"252\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\">Über das Projekt</h2><p data-start=\"254\" data-end=\"576\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><span data-cms-image=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okcompany/web-studio/main/apps/web/public/uploads/img_1777642212608_5729.png\" data-cms-filename=\"222.png\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"cms-image-token\">[222.png]</span>Vollwertige Weblösung für ein italienisches Lieferrestaurant in Siegen, Deutschland.<br data-start=\"338\" data-end=\"341\">Das System ermöglicht es Kunden, die Speisekarte zu durchsuchen, einen Warenkorb zu erstellen und Bestellungen aufzugeben.<br data-start=\"463\" data-end=\"466\">Der Administrator kann Inhalte verwalten, Bestellungen in Echtzeit bearbeiten und Benachrichtigungen erhalten.</p><p data-start=\"578\" data-end=\"638\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\">🔗 <strong data-start=\"581\" data-end=\"598\">Live-Website:</strong> <a data-start=\"599\" data-end=\"638\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_new\" class=\"decorated-link\" href=\"https://pizza-roma-siegen-v2.vercel.app\">https://pizza-roma-siegen-v2.vercel.app<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-rtl-flip=\"\" class=\"block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]\"><use href=\"/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#304883\" fill=\"currentColor\"></use></svg></span></a></p><hr data-start=\"640\" data-end=\"643\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"f2a5u4\" data-start=\"645\" data-end=\"670\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><span data-cms-image=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okcompany/web-studio/main/apps/web/public/uploads/img_1777642240627_3167.png\" data-cms-filename=\"333.png\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"cms-image-token\">[333.png]</span>Funktionen der Website</h2><h3 data-section-id=\"8nv5hq\" data-start=\"672\" data-end=\"690\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\">🛍️ Für Kunden</h3><ul data-start=\"691\" data-end=\"946\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><li data-section-id=\"mtexrn\" data-start=\"691\" data-end=\"761\">Benutzerfreundlicher Warenkorb mit Auswahl von Toppings und Größen</li><li data-section-id=\"1tjs423\" data-start=\"762\" data-end=\"807\">Umschaltung zwischen Deutsch und Russisch</li><li data-section-id=\"b003i1\" data-start=\"808\" data-end=\"851\">Anzeige aktueller Angebote und Aktionen</li><li data-section-id=\"2hpy48\" data-start=\"852\" data-end=\"899\">Informationen zu Liefergebieten und -kosten</li><li data-section-id=\"bx6tcp\" data-start=\"900\" data-end=\"946\">Bestellung mit Schutz vor Bots (ReCAPTCHA)</li></ul><hr data-start=\"948\" data-end=\"951\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><h3 data-section-id=\"t032o8\" data-start=\"953\" data-end=\"979\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><span data-cms-image=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okcompany/web-studio/main/apps/web/public/uploads/img_1777642256738_4069.png\" data-cms-filename=\"444.png\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"cms-image-token\">[444.png]</span>⚙️ Für Administratoren</h3><ul data-start=\"980\" data-end=\"1269\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><li data-section-id=\"a0lv2n\" data-start=\"980\" data-end=\"1029\">Geschütztes Admin-Panel mit Authentifizierung</li><li data-section-id=\"13vohov\" data-start=\"1030\" data-end=\"1103\">Bearbeitung von Menü, Preisen, Beschreibungen und Bildern in Echtzeit</li><li data-section-id=\"8r9ksc\" data-start=\"1104\" data-end=\"1155\">Verwaltung und Aktualisierung von Bestellstatus</li><li data-section-id=\"k7m3xt\" data-start=\"1156\" data-end=\"1224\">Sofortige Benachrichtigungen über neue Bestellungen via Telegram</li><li data-section-id=\"433hwd\" data-start=\"1225\" data-end=\"1269\">Automatisches Speichern aller Änderungen</li></ul><hr data-start=\"1271\" data-end=\"1274\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1tfww54\" data-start=\"1276\" data-end=\"1291\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\">Technologien</h2><p data-start=\"1293\" data-end=\"1425\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><strong data-start=\"1293\" data-end=\"1328\"><span data-cms-image=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okcompany/web-studio/main/apps/web/public/uploads/img_1777642268704_4095.png\" data-cms-filename=\"555.png\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"cms-image-token\">[555.png]</span>Next.js 14 + React + TypeScript</strong><br data-start=\"1328\" data-end=\"1331\">Moderner Technologie-Stack mit Server-Side Rendering für schnelle Ladezeiten und optimale SEO.</p><p data-start=\"1427\" data-end=\"1506\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><strong data-start=\"1427\" data-end=\"1449\">Responsives Design</strong><br data-start=\"1449\" data-end=\"1452\">Optimiert für Smartphones, Tablets und Desktop-Geräte.</p><p data-start=\"1508\" data-end=\"1596\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><strong data-start=\"1508\" data-end=\"1532\">Flüssige Animationen</strong><br data-start=\"1532\" data-end=\"1535\">Framer Motion sorgt für moderne Übergänge und Interaktivität.</p><p data-start=\"1598\" data-end=\"1710\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><strong data-start=\"1598\" data-end=\"1631\">Zuverlässige Datenspeicherung</strong><br data-start=\"1631\" data-end=\"1634\"><span data-cms-image=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okcompany/web-studio/main/apps/web/public/uploads/img_1777642280521_2164.png\" data-cms-filename=\"666.png\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"cms-image-token\">[666.png]</span>Menüdaten werden in GitHub gespeichert und gehen bei Updates nicht verloren.</p><hr data-start=\"1712\" data-end=\"1715\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1em7xgm\" data-start=\"1717\" data-end=\"1728\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\">Ergebnis</h2><p data-start=\"1730\" data-end=\"1928\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\">Eine vollständig einsatzbereite Lieferplattform mit allen notwendigen Funktionen.<br data-start=\"1811\" data-end=\"1814\">Kunden können bequem Essen bestellen, während das Restaurant alle Prozesse effizient über das Admin-Panel steuert.</p><hr data-start=\"1930\" data-end=\"1933\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p data-start=\"1935\" data-end=\"2018\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;\"><em data-start=\"1935\" data-end=\"2016\">Das Projekt wurde als vollwertige Lösung für ein reales Unternehmen entwickelt.</em></p>"
  },
